      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm selling my awesome car and it's looking for a brand new home! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is in really nice shape\u2014perfect for zipping around town or hitting the highway for a weekend getaway. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a charm. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast with it. Come by and take it for a spin!",
