    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is equipped with the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a verified subframe. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing inspection. The engine pulls linearly across the powerband with no hesitation in the high-pressure VANOS system. A mechanically sound example ready for spirited B-road carving or track-day duty.",
      "price": 31500.0,
