    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-performing car that has been treated with care. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy luster, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor rock chips on the hood and a small, two-inch superficial scratch on the passenger side door\u2014typical for a car of this age. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no curb rash. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has never been smoked in; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented service history. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts crisply, and the suspension remains firm and responsive. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brake pads and tires still have plenty of life left. This is a solid, honest vehicle that drives as well as it looks.",
